## Section 25: Micro-Interactions

### 25.1 Hover Effects

```css
/* Button hover - already defined in Section 9 */
.button {
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.button:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
}

/* Card hover */
.card-hover {
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.card-hover:hover {
  transform: scale(1.02);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}
```

### 25.2 Focus Indicators

```css
/* Keyboard focus - WCAG 2.2 AA compliant */
.interactive-element:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid #3b82f6;
  outline-offset: 2px;
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
}

/* Focus within forms */
.input:focus-within {
  ring: 2px;
  ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
  border-color: #3b82f6;
}
```

### 25.3 Click Feedback

```tsx
const ClickableCard = ({ onClick, children }) => {
